<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Anatomy Quest</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@700;800&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #0c0c14;
  --surface: #14141e;
  --surface2: #1c1c2a;
  --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  --border2: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
  --text: #eeecf0;
  --muted: #7a7890;
  --accent: #b8f050;
  --accent2: #7b6ef6;
  --correct: #50f0a0;
  --wrong: #f05050;
  --gold: #f0c840;
}
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  min-height: 100vh;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 15% 15%, rgba(123,110,246,0.08) 0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 85%, rgba(184,240,80,0.06) 0%, transparent 55%);
  pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
}
.wrap {
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
  max-width: 820px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem;
}
.hdr {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}
.logo {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  color: var(--accent);
}
.logo em { color: var(--text); font-style: normal; }
.hdr-stats { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; }
.pill {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 999px;
  color: var(--muted);
  display: flex; gap: 0.35rem; align-items: center;
}
.pill b { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
.screen { display: none; }
.screen.on { display: block; animation: up 0.35s ease; }
@keyframes up { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(14px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }
.hero-title {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.6rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.06;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
}
.hero-title .hi { color: var(--accent); }
.hero-sub {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.65;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  max-width: 480px;
}
.section-label {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}
.chips { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.45rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.chip {
  padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.18s;
  color: var(--muted);
}
.chip:hover { border-color: var(--border2); color: var(--text); }
.chip.on { background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); color: #0c0c14; font-weight: 500; }
.mode-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  gap: 0.75rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.mode-card {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 1.25rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.mode-card::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--card-col, var(--accent2));
}
.mode-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); border-color: var(--border2); }
.mode-card.on { border-color: var(--card-col, var(--accent2)); background: var(--surface2); }
.mode-icon { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
.mode-name {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}
.mode-desc { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }
.btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.18s;
}
.btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: #0c0c14; }
.btn-primary:hover { filter: brightness(1.08); transform: translateY(-1px); }
.btn-primary:disabled { opacity: 0.4; cursor: default; transform: none; }
.btn-ghost {
  background: var(--surface);
  color: var(--text);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--border2); background: var(--surface2); }
.progress-bar-wrap {
  background: var(--surface);
  border-radius: 999px;
  height: 5px;
  margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.progress-bar-fill {
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--accent);
  border-radius: 999px;
  transition: width 0.4s ease;
}
.quiz-meta {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.quiz-topic {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  color: var(--accent2);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  background: rgba(123,110,246,0.12);
  padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(123,110,246,0.2);
}
.quiz-count {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  color: var(--muted);
}
.q-card {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 18px;
  padding: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.q-type-badge {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.q-text { font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 500; }
.q-text strong { color: var(--accent); }
.answers {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 0.65rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
@media (max-width: 540px) { .answers { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
.ans-btn {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 0.9rem 1.1rem;
  text-align: left;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  color: var(--text);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.18s;
  line-height: 1.45;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 0.65rem;
}
.ans-btn:hover:not(:disabled) { border-color: var(--border2); background: var(--surface2); transform: translateY(-1px); }
.ans-btn:disabled { cursor: default; }
.ans-btn.correct { border-color: var(--correct); background: rgba(80,240,160,0.08); color: var(--correct); }
.ans-btn.wrong { border-color: var(--wrong); background: rgba(240,80,80,0.08); color: var(--wrong); }
.ans-key {
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 5px;
  padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 1px;
  color: var(--muted);
}
.ans-btn.correct .ans-key { background: rgba(80,240,160,0.2); color: var(--correct); }
.ans-btn.wrong .ans-key { background: rgba(240,80,80,0.2); color: var(--wrong); }
.feedback-box {
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 1.1rem 1.3rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  display: none;
  animation: up 0.25s ease;
}
.feedback-box.show { display: block; }
.feedback-box.ok { background: rgba(80,240,160,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(80,240,160,0.25); }
.feedback-box.bad { background: rgba(240,80,80,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(240,80,80,0.25); }
.feedback-head {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.feedback-box.ok .feedback-head { color: var(--correct); }
.feedback-box.bad .feedback-head { color: var(--wrong); }
.feedback-body { font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
.quiz-actions { display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 0.75rem; }
.streak-flash {
  position: fixed;
  top: 50%; left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.5);
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--gold);
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 100;
  opacity: 0;
}
.streak-flash.pop { animation: pop 1.2s ease forwards; }
@keyframes pop {
  0%   { opacity:0; transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(0.4); }
  20%  { opacity:1; transform: translate(-50%,-55%) scale(1.15); }
  60%  { opacity:1; transform: translate(-50%,-58%) scale(1); }
  100% { opacity:0; transform: translate(-50%,-70%) scale(0.9); }
}
.results-hero { text-align: center; padding: 3rem 0 2rem; }
.results-score {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(4rem, 12vw, 7rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
}
.results-label { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
.results-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 0.75rem;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}
@media (max-width: 500px) { .results-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
.stat-card {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 1rem;
  text-align: center;
}
.stat-card .sv {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
}
.stat-card .sl { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); }
.results-actions { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.review-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.review-item {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
}
.review-q { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.review-yours { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--wrong); margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
.review-correct { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--correct); }
.divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 2rem 0; }
.timer-bar-wrap {
  height: 3px;
  background: var(--surface2);
  border-radius: 999px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.timer-bar-fill {
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--accent2);
  border-radius: 999px;
  transition: width 1s linear, background 0.3s;
}
.timer-bar-fill.hurry { background: var(--wrong); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="streak-flash" class="streak-flash"></div>

<div class="wrap">
  <div class="hdr">
    <div class="logo">Anatomy<em>Quest</em></div>
    <div class="hdr-stats">
      <div class="pill">🔥 <b id="hdr-streak">0</b> streak</div>
      <div class="pill">⭐ <b id="hdr-score">0</b> pts</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- HOME -->
  <div id="screen-home" class="screen on">
    <h1 class="hero-title">Master<br><span class="hi">Anatomy</span><br>one quiz at a time.</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Muscles, nerves, origins, insertions — pick your topics and test yourself with 60+ questions pulled straight from your lecture notes.</p>

    <div class="section-label">Choose topics</div>
    <div class="chips" id="topic-chips"></div>

    <div class="section-label">Game mode</div>
    <div class="mode-grid" id="mode-grid">
      <div class="mode-card on" data-mode="quiz" style="--card-col:#7b6ef6">
        <div class="mode-icon">🧠</div>
        <div class="mode-name">Quiz</div>
        <div class="mode-desc">Multiple choice — 4 options, pick the right answer. Streak bonuses apply.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="mode-card" data-mode="timed" style="--card-col:#f0c840">
        <div class="mode-icon">⚡</div>
        <div class="mode-name">Speed Round</div>
        <div class="mode-desc">10 seconds per question. Clock is ticking. Faster = more points.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="mode-card" data-mode="survival" style="--card-col:#f05050">
        <div class="mode-icon">❤️</div>
        <div class="mode-name">Survival</div>
        <div class="mode-desc">3 lives. One wrong answer costs you a life. Don't die.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label">Number of questions</div>
    <div class="chips" id="count-chips">
      <div class="chip on" data-val="10">10</div>
      <div class="chip" data-val="20">20</div>
      <div class="chip" data-val="30">30</div>
      <div class="chip" data-val="50">All 60+</div>
    </div>

    <button class="btn btn-primary" id="btn-start" onclick="startGame()">Start Game →</button>
  </div>

  <!-- QUIZ -->
  <div id="screen-quiz" class="screen">
    <div class="progress-bar-wrap">
      <div class="progress-bar-fill" id="progress-fill" style="width:0%"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="quiz-meta">
      <span class="quiz-topic" id="q-topic-label">—</span>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:center">
        <span id="lives-display" style="font-size:1rem;letter-spacing:0.05em"></span>
        <span class="quiz-count" id="q-count-label">1 / 10</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="timer-bar-wrap" id="timer-wrap" style="display:none">
      <div class="timer-bar-fill" id="timer-fill" style="width:100%"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-card">
      <div class="q-type-badge" id="q-type-badge">Origin / Insertion</div>
      <div class="q-text" id="q-text">Loading...</div>
    </div>
    <div class="answers" id="answers-grid"></div>
    <div class="feedback-box" id="feedback-box">
      <div class="feedback-head" id="feedback-head"></div>
      <div class="feedback-body" id="feedback-body"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="quiz-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="quitGame()">Quit</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" id="btn-next" onclick="nextQuestion()" style="display:none">Next →</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- RESULTS -->
  <div id="screen-results" class="screen">
    <div class="results-hero">
      <div class="results-score" id="res-score">0%</div>
      <div class="results-label" id="res-label">—</div>
    </div>
    <div class="results-grid">
      <div class="stat-card"><div class="sv" id="res-correct" style="color:var(--correct)">0</div><div class="sl">Correct</div></div>
      <div class="stat-card"><div class="sv" id="res-wrong" style="color:var(--wrong)">0</div><div class="sl">Wrong</div></div>
      <div class="stat-card"><div class="sv" id="res-streak" style="color:var(--gold)">0</div><div class="sl">Best Streak</div></div>
      <div class="stat-card"><div class="sv" id="res-pts">0</div><div class="sl">Points</div></div>
      <div class="stat-card"><div class="sv" id="res-time">—</div><div class="sl">Avg Speed</div></div>
      <div class="stat-card"><div class="sv" id="res-acc">—</div><div class="sl">Accuracy</div></div>
    </div>
    <div id="review-section" style="display:none">
      <hr class="divider">
      <div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:1rem">Review wrong answers</div>
      <div class="review-list" id="review-list"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="results-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="showScreen('home')">Menu</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="startGame()">Play Again →</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
const QUESTIONS = [
  // GLUTEAL REGION
  { topic:"Gluteal Region", type:"Origin", q:"Where does <strong>Gluteus Maximus</strong> originate?", a:"Posterior surface of the ilium, sacrum & coccyx", wrong:["Iliac fossa of the pelvis","Anterior surface of the sacrum","Ischial tuberosity"], fact:"Gluteus Maximus is the largest and most superficial gluteal muscle." },
  { topic:"Gluteal Region", type:"Insertion", q:"Where do the <strong>superior fibres</strong> of Gluteus Maximus insert?", a:"Iliotibial tract", wrong:["Gluteal tuberosity of femur","Greater trochanter","Lesser trochanter"], fact:"The inferior fibres insert into the gluteal tuberosity of the femur." },
  { topic:"Gluteal Region", type:"Nerve", q:"Which nerve innervates <strong>Gluteus Maximus</strong>?", a:"Inferior gluteal nerve (L5, S1, S2)", wrong:["Superior gluteal nerve (L4, L5, S1)","Obturator nerve (L2-L4)","Sciatic nerve (L4-S3)"], fact:"The superior gluteal nerve innervates Gluteus Medius, Minimus and TFL." },
  { topic:"Gluteal Region", type:"Action", q:"What is the primary action of <strong>Gluteus Medius & Minimus</strong>?", a:"Abduction and medial rotation of the hip", wrong:["Extension and lateral rotation","Adduction of the thigh","Flexion at the hip joint"], fact:"Gluteus Maximus is the main extensor and assists lateral rotation." },
  { topic:"Gluteal Region", type:"Insertion", q:"Where does <strong>Gluteus Medius</strong> insert?", a:"Lateral surface of the greater trochanter", wrong:["Anterior aspect of the greater trochanter","Iliotibial tract","Quadrate tubercle on intertrochanteric crest"], fact:"Gluteus Minimus inserts on the anterior aspect of the greater trochanter." },
  { topic:"Gluteal Region", type:"Fact", q:"<strong>Piriformis</strong> is a key landmark because the sciatic nerve emerges:", a:"Inferior to piriformis", wrong:["Superior to piriformis","Medial to piriformis","Through the piriformis muscle"], fact:"Piriformis is the most superior of the deep gluteal muscles, originating from the anterior surface of the sacrum." },
  { topic:"Gluteal Region", type:"Origin", q:"Where does <strong>Quadratus Femoris</strong> originate?", a:"Ischial tuberosity", wrong:["Ischial spine","Obturator membrane","Anterior surface of sacrum"], fact:"Quadratus Femoris is the most inferior deep gluteal muscle." },
  { topic:"Gluteal Region", type:"Insertion", q:"Where does <strong>Quadratus Femoris</strong> insert — unlike the other deep gluteal muscles?", a:"Quadrate tubercle on the intertrochanteric crest", wrong:["Posterosuperior aspect of the greater trochanter","Iliotibial tract","Medial lip of the intertubercular groove"], fact:"All other deep gluteal muscles insert on the posterosuperior aspect of the greater trochanter." },
  { topic:"Gluteal Region", type:"Origin", q:"Where does <strong>Tensor Fascia Lata</strong> originate?", a:"ASIS (Anterior Superior Iliac Spine)", wrong:["AIIS (Anterior Inferior Iliac Spine)","Iliac crest","Posterior surface of ilium"], fact:"TFL inserts into the anterior aspect of the iliotibial tract and is innervated by the superior gluteal nerve." },
  { topic:"Gluteal Region", type:"Nerve", q:"Which nerve innervates <strong>Obturator Externus</strong>?", a:"Obturator nerve (L2-L4)", wrong:["Nerve to quadratus femoris","Superior gluteal nerve","Inferior gluteal nerve"], fact:"Obturator Externus is sometimes classed as a deep gluteal muscle and also adducts the thigh." },
  // ANTERIOR THIGH
  { topic:"Thigh — Anterior", type:"Nerve", q:"Which nerve innervates all <strong>Quadriceps</strong> muscles?", a:"Femoral nerve (L2-L4)", wrong:["Obturator nerve (L2-L4)","Sciatic nerve (L4-S3)","Musculocutaneous nerve (C5-C7)"], fact:"Pectineus also receives a branch from the obturator nerve." },
  { topic:"Thigh — Anterior", type:"Insertion", q:"Where do all <strong>Quadriceps</strong> muscles insert?", a:"Base of the patella via the quadriceps tendon", wrong:["Head of fibula","Medial tibial condyle","Pes anserinus on the proximal tibia"], fact:"The tendon continues as the patellar ligament to the tibial tuberosity." },
  { topic:"Thigh — Anterior", type:"Fact", q:"Which quadriceps muscle is the <strong>only one</strong> that crosses the hip joint?", a:"Rectus Femoris", wrong:["Vastus Medialis","Vastus Lateralis","Vastus Intermedius"], fact:"Rectus Femoris originates from the AIIS and groove above the acetabulum, allowing it to also flex the thigh at the hip." },
  { topic:"Thigh — Anterior", type:"Origin", q:"Where does <strong>Vastus Medialis</strong> originate?", a:"Intertrochanteric line & medial lip of the linea aspera", wrong:["Greater trochanter & lateral lip of linea aspera","Anterior and lateral surfaces of femoral shaft","AIIS and groove above acetabulum"], fact:"The VMO fibres resist lateral displacement of the patella." },
  { topic:"Thigh — Anterior", type:"Origin", q:"Where does <strong>Sartorius</strong> originate, and what makes it notable?", a:"ASIS — it is the longest muscle in the body", wrong:["AIIS — it crosses three joints","Ischial tuberosity — it is a hamstring","Iliac crest — it stabilises the pelvis"], fact:"Sartorius inserts into the pes anserinus alongside gracilis and semitendinosus." },
  { topic:"Thigh — Anterior", type:"Insertion", q:"Where does <strong>Iliopsoas</strong> insert?", a:"Lesser trochanter of the femur", wrong:["Greater trochanter of the femur","Medial tibial condyle","AIIS"], fact:"Iliopsoas comprises psoas major and iliacus. It is the prime flexor of the hip." },
  { topic:"Thigh — Anterior", type:"Fact", q:"<strong>Pectineus</strong> forms the base of the femoral triangle. What is its action?", a:"Adducts and flexes the thigh at the hip", wrong:["Extends and laterally rotates the thigh","Abducts and medially rotates the hip","Flexes the knee and adducts the thigh"], fact:"Pectineus originates from the pectineal line on the anterior surface of the superior pubic ramus." },
